snippet.title: Amber Heard Could Face 3 Years In Prison For Faking Evidence
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Could Face 3 Years In Prison For Faking Evidence
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

The case against amber heard has just taken another turn. She not only would owe jonny depp 50 million dollars if he wins. If Johnny Depp’s legal defense team can prove that amber heard falsified evidence against him, she faces some serious jail time. One of the main arguments in johnny depp’s case against amber is that her accusations about him are all part of an elaborate hoax, elaborate, but poorly executed. Lets get right down to the facts, but first, the intro.
